summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2015 DODGE JOURNEY. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE FRONT SEAT PASSENGER SIDE HEADREST AIR BAG DEPLOYED AFTER THE DOOR WAS CLOSED. THERE WERE NO WARNING INDICATORS ILLUMINATED. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO LANDERS DODGE JEEP CHRYSLER WHERE IT WAS DIAGNOSED THAT THE HEADREST AIR BAG DEPLOYED AND NEEDED TO BE RESET DUE TO THE SRS SYSTEM ACTIVATING. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS APPROXIMATELY 39,042.
